snippet.title: Killing Garfield ft. Amber (7-14-2016) - Cum Town (EP 10)
snippet.description:
"Sorry for the delay everyone, i was actually busy at uh, the black people matter protests. I was protesting for black people so I didn't have time to upload this one, which was also delayed because Kurt Metzger rescheduled. Amber Frost (of the Baffler and some other places) joined in. Amber is cool but we wasted her insight by making her talk about gay shit that we like. We're gonna do a bonus episode this week to make up for it."
Thanks for listening to the Cum Town Podcast.
Support the boys at www.patreon.com/cumtown/ and check out some merch at CumTownStore.com or by searching "Cum Town Podcast" on Amazon.
